            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-8 sm:mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed px-2">
                Specializing in React, Next.js, and AI integration. Building scalable web applications and teaching teams to adopt emerging technologies.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 justify-center items-center px-4">
                <a href="/work" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-gray-900 text-white px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors text-center font-medium">
                    View My Work
                </a>
                <a href="/contact" class="w-full sm:w-auto border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors text-center font-medium">
                    Get In Touch
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    
    <!-- Featured Projects - Bento Style -->
    <main>
        <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6" aria-labelledby="featured-work-heading">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
                <h2 id="featured-work-heading" class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-gray-900 mb-12 sm:mb-16 text-center">
                    Selected Work
                </h2>
            
